[
  {
    "type": "h1",
    "text": "INTRODUCTION TO DFT",
    "id": "h.opfadh86grqx",
    "html": "<span class=\"c6 c23\">INTRODUCTION TO DFT</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "(Design For Testability – Beginner Level)",
    "id": "h.vtp5fgashlla",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">(Design For Testability – Beginner Level)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "1️⃣ Importance of Testing (WHY testing is needed?)",
    "id": "h.vfxhnf2bdbqa",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">1️⃣ Importance of Testing (WHY testing is needed?)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why is testing mandatory in VLSI?",
    "id": "h.ob7yq42ylpyt",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why is testing mandatory in VLSI?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>As </span><span class=\"c6\">technology node reduces</span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;(7nm, 5nm, 3nm):<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span>Transistors become </span><span class=\"c6 c19\">very small<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span>Manufacturing becomes </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">more complex<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Even a </span><span class=\"c6\">tiny dust particle</span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;can:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Short two wires<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Break a connection (open fault)<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "100% defect-free manufacturing is NOT possible",
    "html": "<span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"c19 c6\">100% defect-free manufacturing is NOT possible</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why we test chips?",
    "id": "h.d6i7c87v4k78",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why we test chips?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Some defects are </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">unavoidable<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Testing helps:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span>Identify </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">good chips<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span>Reject </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">bad chips<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Faulty chips must </span><span class=\"c6\">NOT</span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;reach customers<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Product Quality Depends On",
    "id": "h.wh8kz0rrp2u",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Product Quality Depends On</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "table",
    "content": "<tbody><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c28\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c17\"><span class=\"c6\">Parameter</span></p></td><td class=\"c26\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c17\"><span class=\"c6\">Meaning</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c28\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Test Cost</span></p></td><td class=\"c26\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Cost spent on testing</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c28\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Test Time</span></p></td><td class=\"c26\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Time taken to test each chip</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c28\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Test Quality</span></p></td><td class=\"c26\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">How many faults are detected</span></p></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Goal: ✔ Low cost ✔ Less time ✔ High fault detection",
    "html": "<span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"c6\">Goal:<br></span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;✔ Low cost<br> ✔ Less time<br> ✔ High fault detection</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image9.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "2️⃣ What is DFT (Design For Testability)?",
    "id": "h.ifbgkfxkkb5z",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">2️⃣ What is DFT (Design For Testability)?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Definition (Simple Words)",
    "id": "h.9c99t3quogan",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Definition (Simple Words)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "DFT is the extra logic added to a chip during the design stage to make post-manufacturing testing possible.",
    "html": "<span class=\"c19 c6\">DFT is the extra logic added to a chip during the design stage to make post-manufacturing testing possible.</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Key Points",
    "id": "h.lllq6gg7rx2b",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Key Points</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>DFT is added </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">before fabrication<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">It helps test:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Internal flip-flops<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Internal nets<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Memory elements<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Manufacturing is </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">not error-free<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">So testing after manufacturing is compulsory<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Important Clarification",
    "id": "h.bik08t208yt1",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Important Clarification</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "DFT does NOT repair the chip  DFT only detects whether chip is GOOD or BAD",
    "html": "<span>&nbsp;DFT does </span><span class=\"c6\">NOT repair</span><span>&nbsp;the chip<br> &nbsp;DFT only </span><span class=\"c6\">detects</span><span class=\"c0\">&nbsp;whether chip is GOOD or BAD</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "DFT is:",
    "id": "h.luiyhdkyqyog",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">DFT is:</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Detection → YES<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Localization → NO<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Repair → NO<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image6.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "3️⃣ Difference Between Verification and Testing",
    "id": "h.ryjko05aywpb",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">3️⃣ Difference Between Verification and Testing</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Functional Verification",
    "id": "h.sbo8he6kf4y7",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Functional Verification</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Done </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">before fabrication<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Uses </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">testbench<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Checks design logic correctness<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Testing (DFT)",
    "id": "h.1fwm81p1okg",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Testing (DFT)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Done </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">after fabrication<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Checks </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">manufacturing defects<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Uses </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">test patterns<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image3.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "4️⃣ Faults, Defects, Errors (VERY IMPORTANT)",
    "id": "h.gvc3cq6e0nhx",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">4️⃣ Faults, Defects, Errors (VERY IMPORTANT)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Defect",
    "id": "h.qii9mhodhcfs",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Defect</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Physical problem in silicon<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Example:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Broken wire<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Short circuit<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Fault",
    "id": "h.unixpt9mdtb7",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Fault</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Logical model of defect<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Example:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Stuck-at-0<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Stuck-at-1<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Error",
    "id": "h.7h6dt9hfnwfx",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Error</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Wrong output seen at chip pin<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Defect → Fault → Error",
    "html": "<span><br> </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">Defect → Fault → Error</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image14.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "5️⃣ Fault Models (Core Concept of DFT)",
    "id": "h.1abyp4uoc482",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">5️⃣ Fault Models (Core Concept of DFT)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why Fault Models?",
    "id": "h.rfgdkwajzn19",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why Fault Models?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">We cannot see inside silicon<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>So we </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">model defects logically<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Most common model: </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">Stuck-At Fault<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Stuck-At-1 Fault",
    "id": "h.ke0suki8xp9r",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Stuck-At-1 Fault</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Net always reads logic ‘1’<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Even if we drive ‘0’<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Stuck-At-0 Fault",
    "id": "h.u47zkphcg0jn",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Stuck-At-0 Fault</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Net always reads logic ‘0’<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Even if we drive ‘1’<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Testing a Net N2",
    "id": "h.mu3cp0nr53if",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Testing a Net N2</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "table",
    "content": "<tbody><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c25\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c17\"><span class=\"c6\">Test</span></p></td><td class=\"c22\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c17\"><span class=\"c6\">Purpose</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c25\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Drive N2 = 0</span></p></td><td class=\"c22\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Check stuck-at-1</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c25\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Drive N2 = 1</span></p></td><td class=\"c22\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Check stuck-at-0</span></p></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image18.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "6️⃣ Controllability & Observability",
    "id": "h.pllwv3crlvs8",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">6️⃣ Controllability &amp; Observability</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Controllability",
    "id": "h.ricwkzd0h0oz",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Controllability</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Ability to force a node to 0 or 1",
    "html": "<span class=\"c0\">Ability to force a node to 0 or 1</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Observability",
    "id": "h.g3u4pedw3lp",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Observability</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Ability to see the value of a node at output",
    "html": "<span class=\"c0\">Ability to see the value of a node at output</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why DFT is needed?",
    "id": "h.stwv3uk2de7x",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why DFT is needed?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Internal nodes are </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">not directly visible<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Only chip pins are visible<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>DFT provides </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">path to control &amp; observe<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image16.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "7️⃣ Fault Simulation & Fault Coverage",
    "id": "h.y4an0rh68ex6",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">7️⃣ Fault Simulation &amp; Fault Coverage</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Fault Simulation",
    "id": "h.7t5oivr01gg6",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Fault Simulation</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Insert faults </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">intentionally<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Run test patterns<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Check if fault is detected<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Fault Coverage Formula",
    "id": "h.hg0voif0ql8k",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Fault Coverage Formula</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Fault Coverage=Detected FaultsTotal Faults×100Fault\\ Coverage = \\frac{Detected\\ Faults}{Total\\ Faults} \\times 100Fault Coverage=Total FaultsDetected Faults​×100",
    "html": "<span>Fault Coverage=Detected FaultsTotal Faults×100Fault\\ Coverage = \\frac{Detected\\ Faults}{Total\\ Faults} \\times 100Fault Coverage=Total FaultsDetected Faults​×100</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Industry Expectation",
    "id": "h.b10a6n5maj2i",
    "html": "<span class=\"c6 c9\">Industry Expectation</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">95% fault coverage<br><br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Some designs target 99%+<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "8️⃣ Types of Defects in VLSI",
    "id": "h.pjw160pftl9j",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">8️⃣ Types of Defects in VLSI</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Process Defects",
    "id": "h.mqlhfhka458o",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Process Defects</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Missing vias<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Shorts<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Opens<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Material Defects",
    "id": "h.5a02l8f9pde2",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Material Defects</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Crystal imperfections<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Impurities<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Aging Defects",
    "id": "h.l3p2xstb7evx",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Aging Defects</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Electromigration<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Oxide breakdown<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Package Defects",
    "id": "h.oxtiicjgp1lm",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Package Defects</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Broken pins<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Seal leaks<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image8.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "9️⃣ Major Types of Faults",
    "id": "h.emp8o2m9an5u",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">9️⃣ Major Types of Faults</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Structural Faults",
    "id": "h.uamvgit5a7h4",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Structural Faults</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Due to manufacturing<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Shorts, opens<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Transition Faults",
    "id": "h.3tmhbtoqqavn",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Transition Faults</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Signal does not switch fast enough<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Related to:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Setup time<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Hold time<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image5.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "🔟 Scan Design (MOST IMPORTANT DFT TOPIC)",
    "id": "h.b2wnj8wpc4kp",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">🔟 Scan Design (MOST IMPORTANT DFT TOPIC)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why Scan Design?",
    "id": "h.hwn94kujpjyh",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why Scan Design?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Flip-flops hide internal states<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span>Scan converts flip-flops into </span><span class=\"c19 c6\">shift register<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Scan Chain Components",
    "id": "h.uw2egrlwiugo",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Scan Chain Components</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "table",
    "content": "<tbody><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c27\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c17\"><span class=\"c6\">Signal</span></p></td><td class=\"c21\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c17\"><span class=\"c6\">Purpose</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c27\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Scan In (SI)</span></p></td><td class=\"c21\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Shift data in</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c27\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Scan Out (SO)</span></p></td><td class=\"c21\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Shift data out</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c27\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Scan Enable (SE)</span></p></td><td class=\"c21\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Select test/functional</span></p></td></tr><tr class=\"c15\"><td class=\"c27\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Clock</span></p></td><td class=\"c21\" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\"><p class=\"c14\"><span class=\"c0\">Shift &amp; capture</span></p></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Functional Mode",
    "id": "h.6r5p5u8r7wbz",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Functional Mode</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Normal operation<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">SE = 0<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Test Mode",
    "id": "h.2kl9h61ojo54",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Test Mode</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Scan enabled<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">SE = 1<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image15.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "1️⃣1️⃣ Scan Stitching",
    "id": "h.n89r5pd2fx8n",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">1️⃣1️⃣ Scan Stitching</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "What is Scan Stitching?",
    "id": "h.bcgku1ly110r",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">What is Scan Stitching?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Connecting flip-flops serially<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Forms scan chains<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why Scan Stitching Needed?",
    "id": "h.6zjx1vnoo7l",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why Scan Stitching Needed?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Access internal flops<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Improve controllability &amp; observability<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Enable ATPG<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Problems Without Reordering",
    "id": "h.nl1h7s3yo8fg",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Problems Without Reordering</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Long wirelength<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Congestion<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Routing issues<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Scan Chain Reordering",
    "id": "h.jn7ev3ca7dc",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Scan Chain Reordering</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Reorder flops based on placement<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Reduces:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Wirelength<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Congestion<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Hold issues<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image12.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "1️⃣2️⃣ Scan Chain Parameters",
    "id": "h.vlryh5glbmal",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">1️⃣2️⃣ Scan Chain Parameters</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Scan Length",
    "id": "h.87z98efhdot7",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Scan Length</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Number of flops in one chain<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Trade-off:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Long chain → less IO, more time<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Short chain → more IO, less time<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Scan Polarity",
    "id": "h.b3g1q6y41cdr",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Scan Polarity</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Active high / Active low scan enable<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Must match library cells<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Scan DEF File",
    "id": "h.ft4i5hhaf4r2",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Scan DEF File</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Contains scan chain info<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Required during physical design<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
