  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "7️⃣ Scan Compression (High-Level)",
    "id": "h.vsknk4tjpnrb",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">7️⃣ Scan Compression (High-Level)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Problem Without Compression",
    "id": "h.5unmq2fxawz5",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Problem Without Compression</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Too many test vectors<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Long tester time<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">High memory usage<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Scan Compression",
    "id": "h.l4i6j9yt7jnp",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Scan Compression</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Compress input patterns<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Decompress on-chip<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Compress output response<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Huge test time reduction",
    "html": "<span>&nbsp;</span><span class=\"c19 c6\">Huge test time reduction</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image4.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "8️⃣ DFT for Memory – MBIST (Intro Level)",
    "id": "h.tvjrjfrzfooa",
    "html": "<span class=\"c6 c11\">8️⃣ DFT for Memory – MBIST (Intro Level)</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "What is MBIST?",
    "id": "h.srim80326pbh",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">What is MBIST?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "p",
    "text": "Memory Built-In Self Test",
    "html": "<span class=\"c0\">Memory Built-In Self Test</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "Why MBIST?",
    "id": "h.ovsnifi7ge00",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">Why MBIST?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Memories occupy large chip area<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Scan cannot efficiently test memories<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "MBIST Tests:",
    "id": "h.9jrgkn8yio7l",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">MBIST Tests:</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Stuck-at faults<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Address faults<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Coupling faults<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "img",
    "src": "images/image17.png",
    "alt": ""
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h2",
    "text": "9️⃣ Boundary Scan (JTAG) – High Level",
    "id": "h.si3qpkiipmiu",
    "html": "<span class=\"c11 c6\">9️⃣ Boundary Scan (JTAG) – High Level</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "What is Boundary Scan?",
    "id": "h.nvb8z9g5wbz9",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">What is Boundary Scan?</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Test IO pins<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Used for:<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Board-level testing<br></span></li><li class=\"c2 c7 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">Debugging<br></span></li>"
  },
  {
    "type": "hr"
  },
  {
    "type": "h3",
    "text": "IEEE Standard",
    "id": "h.szv083r8iy3t",
    "html": "<span class=\"c9 c6\">IEEE Standard</span>"
  },
  {
    "type": "ul",
    "html": "<li class=\"c2 c3 li-bullet-0\"><span class=\"c0\">IEEE 1149.1 (JTAG)<br></span></li>"
  },
